# Task types — the four the exam names

| Task | Runs | Compute |
|---|---|---|
| **Notebook** | `.ipynb` (Workspace / Git Folder) | cluster (job/all-purpose/serverless) |
| **SQL** | query · alert · file · dashboard | **SQL warehouse** |
| **Pipeline** | declarative pipeline (ex-DLT) | pipeline-managed |
| **Dashboard** | refresh AI/BI dashboard | **SQL warehouse** |

- **SQL task** has 4 sub-variants (query most common)

## Secondary — recognise these

- **JAR / Python script / wheel** (bundles, module 07) · **dbt** · **Run job** (nested)
- **`for_each`** (loop) · **`if/else`** (branch)

**Match artifact → task type:** dashboard → **Dashboard task**; pipeline → **Pipeline task** (self-managed compute).
